com.ikarus.solartaxi.level

Class Level

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ikarus.solartaxi.level.Level
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Level1, Level2

    public abstract class Level
extends java.lang.Object
    Storage class for references defining a level/world in the game NOTE: for now, levels should be defined in subclass constructors (hardcoded) by setting all protected class fields accordingly this is just a quick solution, if a lot of levels were to be included, it might be nicer to use a custom XML definition and parser
    Author:
    Nikolaus Leopold, Sebastian Kirchner
